goals__remit:
-    To represent the interests of its Members (as defined hereinafter); 
-    To act as a spokesman for the Expanded Clay Aggregate industry at a European level, and particularly vis-à-vis the institutions of the European Union (hereinafter referred to as the "EU"); 
-    To communicate the views of the Expanded Clay Aggregate industry on all relevant developments in relation to technical, environmental, energy and promotional issues; 
-    To maintain a permanent dialogue with other industry associations in Europe
